Title: Hotel for Strangers
Actors: Petr Cepek, Tatána Fischerová, Marta Krásová, Vladimír Smeral
Plot: Once, a young poet (Petr Cepek) has been killed in the Art Nouveau setting of the castle The World. Later, his diary is found and the brief and incoherent notes became the basis for the story of the events preceding the murder.
